<paragraph id="884F36F08617FFCAFF7DFA4ECA46FA03" blockId="5.[192,1440,1313,1498]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">
<emphasis id="BA84EAE28617FFCAFF7DFA4EC92FFA43" bold="true" box="[192,323,1410,1434]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described from a series of 
<specimenCount id="9EF6FD798617FFCAFCF7FA4ECBD2FA43" box="[842,958,1410,1434]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" type="male">four male</specimenCount>
